cofh.lib.gui

Class GuiBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • GuiContainer
      • cofh.lib.gui.GuiBase

  • public abstract class GuiBase
extends GuiContainer
    Base class for a modular GUIs. Works with Elements ElementBase and Tabs TabBase which are both modular elements.
